function Get-UniFiIsAlive
{
   <#
         .SYNOPSIS
         Use a simple API call to see if the session is alive

         .DESCRIPTION
         Use a simple API call to see if the session is alive

         .PARAMETER UnifiSite
         UniFi Site as configured. The default is: default

